name: 26,938,085 views
description: This is one of the first explorations, made five years ago, of the style I use today.  I was experimenting with 3D and lines.  I posted it on giphy and to date it has been viewed almost 27 million times.  I do not really understand why...but it feels nice as an artist to know that many people looked at something you made. @dkoblesky
